rComments: Gave a list of questions that helped when reading the textbook. I mean who does that? He's my boy yo!

He's good and bad at the same time. Lectures are really boring and a lot of the time, you don't understand what he's talking about. Dreadful textbook written in old English. But his tests are easy, since he gives you a list of possible questions beforehand. Heavily weighted assignments, but just make sure you have a thesis and you'll be good.

Nice Professor, test expectations very clear, gives helpful questions in advance, do them if you want to score high! good for students who like to memorize and regurgitate, no critical thinking required or encouraged, no class discussions even at 300 level, textbook use only, no academic journals.
Amazing Prof. Really approachable and very easy marker. Very clear on what is expected on the test. Tests are straightforward
